item.title: How do I change the starting gear and here Starter packs
item.dc:creator: @r34p4g3pk r34p4g3pk
item.description:
@r34p4g3pk wrote:

Well find a few item id’s that you start out with, and then go into player.java and hold c+f until a search window pops up, search the code and you should find the results, you can either delete them or change the id’s.

Hope i helped :D.
